    <item>
      <title>NASA Citizen Scientist: Asteroid Discovery</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/asteroid-discovery/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/asteroid-discovery/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In 2019, I participated in a citizen science initiative with the NASA Jet Propulsion Laboratory (JPL). Through meticulous data analysis, I successfully identified three provisional asteroids. This achievement remains a cornerstone of my commitment to aerospace exploration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
